    {
      "id": "PopularPost302113",
      "post_content": "It didn't ever work the way aznxknightz described, but there *was* a brief issue with Fire Whip when it was released: due to the wording, the controller of the enchantment decided when to tap the creature (as it was an activation cost for the enchantment). This could be abused with things like [Ray of Command](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ray of Command) to slap it on an opponent's creature and still have control of the tap ability, essentially making you into the *Magic* version of the guy who grabs someone's hand and repeatedly pushes it into their face while asking them why they keep hitting themselves.   \n  \nIf I recall correctly, they errata'd the wording within a few weeks of release to give the enchanted creature the tap ability, and every similar card since then has used the same wording.",
      "posted_by": "TheLegendary",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost302113\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">It didn't ever work the way aznxknightz described, but there <i>was</i> a brief issue with Fire Whip when it was released: due to the wording, the controller of the enchantment decided when to tap the creature (as it was an activation cost for the enchantment). This could be abused with things like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ray of Command\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ray of Command\">Ray of Command</a> to slap it on an opponent's creature and still have control of the tap ability, essentially making you into the <i>Magic</i> version of the guy who grabs someone's hand and repeatedly pushes it into their face while asking them why they keep hitting themselves. <br/><br/>If I recall correctly, they errata'd the wording within a few weeks of release to give the enchanted creature the tap ability, and every similar card since then has used the same wording.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '302113'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2799\">TheLegendary</span>\r\n                                (2/28/2013 4:37:07 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"post