      "id": "PopularPost111732",
      "post_content": "Back in the day, once this card hits the field the game is over. Why? Read the card again. The text reads: Tap Enchanted creature: ....\n  \nIt didn't give the creature the tap ability and thus players were allowed to tap the tapped creature as many times as they liked and win the game like that. Of course it has been errated, now it's just a better [power of fire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=power of fire).",
